---
import homeHero from '../assets/home-hero.png';
---

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero bg-base-100 mt-8 max-h-full w-screen lg:mt-16 lg:px-10">
    <div
      class="hero-content w-full max-w-full flex-col gap-12 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:justify-between lg:p-0"
    >
      <div id="hero-right-side" class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-end lg:gap-28">
        <img src={homeHero.src} class="max-w-full xl:max-w-lg" />
        <svg
          class="hidden xl:block"
          width="9"
          height="115"
          viewBox="0 0 9 115"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <rect width="9" height="115" rx="4.5" fill="#D7561D"></rect>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div id="hero-left-side" class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div id="hero-title-container max-w-2xl">
          <h1 class="font-hepta text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">
            A <span class="text-accent">Raposa</span> tem algo a dizer.
          </h1>
          <svg
            width="125"
            height="125"
            viewBox="0 0 125 125"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M43.017 65.3307L114.283 65.2804L95.5019 83.8838C94.3281 85.0465 94.3207 86.6042 95.4834 87.778C96.6461 88.9518 98.2038 88.9592 99.3776 87.7965L122.854 64.5424C124.028 63.3797 124.035 61.822 122.873 60.6481L99.6186 37.1716C98.4559 35.9977 96.8982 35.9903 95.7243 37.153C94.5505 38.3157 94.5431 39.8734 95.7058 41.0473L114.309 59.8285L43.4342 59.4912C41.8765 59.4838 40.7027 60.6465 40.6953 62.2042C40.6878 63.7618 41.8505 64.9357 43.017 65.3307Z"
              fill="#D7561D"></path>
            <path
              d="M0.9745 62.0142C0.967086 63.5719 2.12979 64.7457 3.68748 64.7531L30.9471 64.8829C32.5048 64.8903 33.6786 63.7276 33.686 62.1699C33.6897 61.391 33.3021 60.9997 32.527 60.2172C31.7519 59.4346 31.3643 59.0434 30.5855 59.0397L3.32586 58.9099C2.93459 59.2975 1.36948 60.8478 0.9745 62.0142Z"
              fill="#101010"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div id="hero-description-container" class="mt-7 max-w-2xl flex-col gap-11 lg:mt-14">
          <button
            class="btn btn-accent text-secondary font-montserrat text-l h-11 max-w-2xs rounded-lg text-lg font-medium"
            >EXPLORE AS PRODUÇÕES</button
          >
          <p class="font-syne py-6 text-justify text-2xl">
            O TEI é o espaço de criação do curso de Jornalismo da PUC Minas Poços de Caldas. Aqui,
            cada estudante transforma ideias em som, narrativa e experiência.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div id="hero-see-more-container" class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 lg:mt-16">
          <svg
            width="40"
            height="38"
            viewBox="0 0 40 38"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <rect x="0.5" y="0.5" width="39" height="37" rx="9.5" fill="white" stroke="black"
            ></rect>
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              clip-rule="evenodd"
